 mọi buồn vui, cùng nhau trưởng thành. Sau khi tốt nghiệp cấp ba mọi người chia nhau mỗi người mỗi ngã.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"78986","season":1,"vote_average":9,"vote_count":9},"modified":"2023-06-15T19:20:42.000Z","cast":["Lý Lan Địch","Trương Tân Thành","Li Qian","Zhou Chengao","Tào Ân Tề"],"director":["沙漠"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Lý Lan Địch","name_vi":"Lý Lan Địch","name_original":"Li Landi","tmdb_id":1909812,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a5ifktKg6n6xSSHOKmpJJshPqIk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1909812"},{"name":"Trương Tân Thành","name_vi":"Trương Tân Thành","name_original":"Zhang Xincheng","tmdb_id":2027708,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mpCVPsEvnMUkmMd1IN1xsBJpk7r.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2027708"},{"name":"Li Qian","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Li Qian","tmdb_id":3275451,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pYBFfZ2B3RaCU1xsSXVb7owZUlx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3275451"},{"name":"Zhou Chengao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhou Chengao","tmdb_id":2027709,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/42VTjPUGzHoiIOg8MNc5fVEmQoF.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2027709"},{"name":"Tào Ân Tề","name_vi":"Tào Ân Tề","name_original":"Vincent Cao","tmdb_id":2027714,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mPq283zAuBLPKs1L8ygATpHbq0R.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2027714"}],"keywords":[],"tmdb_checked":true,"pubjs_url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gotvtop102/pjs102@main/pubjs/xi/xin-chao-ngay-xua-ay.json"}